{"tid":891684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港眾志 聲明：聯合國疑受中方壓力 香港眾志意見書被刪 促請人權事務高級專員辦事處公開解釋】","createTime":"2018-11-06T10:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T16:19:47.000Z","uid":153615,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"084a4188c272ead20479915ba4c1e51aaf9e7e02","tid":891684,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/posts/978640812344741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fposts%2F978640812344741&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9581adcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/posts/978640812344741</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGGTjXr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGGTjXr.png&h=3f7f103d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據普遍定期審議（Universal Periodic Review），聯合國人權理事會（United Nation Human Right Council）會在11月6日召開會議，由眾多國家共同審議中國人權狀況。<br />\n<br />\n公民團體可就著中國、香港及澳門的人權狀況呈交意見書，給予聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處（The Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights）發佈團體摘要（Stakeholder Summary），並轉交相關意見書予聯合國成員國了解民間訴求。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處在9月3日公佈團體摘要報告（<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/EN/HRBodies/UPR/Pages/CNIndex.aspx），香港眾志因已呈交意見書（http://bit.ly/demosistoUPR）而被列入「團體名單」，當中重點詳述政府取消議員資格和監禁政治犯的狀況；而我們提出改善香港人權自由的建議，亦被引述於改善措施的章節當中。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2FHRBodies%2FUPR%2FPages%2FCNIndex.aspx%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9B%A0%E5%B7%B2%E5%91%88%E4%BA%A4%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B%E6%9B%B8%EF%BC%88http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FdemosistoUPR%EF%BC%89%E8%80%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E%E8%A9%B3%E8%BF%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%8A%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%80%E6%B3%81%EF%BC%9B%E8%80%8C%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A6%E8%A2%AB%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E6%96%BC%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%A0%E7%AF%80%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%82&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5f376b7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ohchr.org/EN/HRBodies/UPR/Pages/CNIndex.aspx），香港眾志因已呈交意見書（http://bit.ly/demosistoUPR）而被列入「團體名單」，當中重點詳述政府取消議員資格和監禁政治犯的狀況；而我們提出改善香港人權自由的建議，亦被引述於改善措施的章節當中。</a><br />\n<br />\n然而，「團體摘要報告（原稿）」（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/uprchina1-chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fuprchina1-chi&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0140ed53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/uprchina1-chi</a> / <a href=\"http://bit.ly/uprchina1-eng）在公佈後數天便遭到移除；事隔多個星期，聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處在10月16日重新上載的「團體摘要報告（訂稿）」（http://bit.ly/upr-china-chi-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fuprchina1-eng%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%BE%8C%E6%95%B8%E5%A4%A9%E4%BE%BF%E9%81%AD%E5%88%B0%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%EF%BC%9B%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%AB%98%E7%B4%9A%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95%E5%9C%A810%E6%9C%8816%E6%97%A5%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%88%E8%A8%82%E7%A8%BF%EF%BC%89%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%88http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fupr-china-chi-2&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e0146def\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/uprchina1-eng）在公佈後數天便遭到移除；事隔多個星期，聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處在10月16日重新上載的「團體摘要報告（訂稿）」（http://bit.ly/upr-china-chi-2</a> / <a href=\"http://bit.ly/upr-china-eng-2），卻明顯出現大幅度的修改。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fupr-china-eng-2%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%BB%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E3%80%82&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5f9174b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/upr-china-eng-2），卻明顯出現大幅度的修改。</a><br />\n<br />\n除了刪去引述香港眾志的段落，聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處更在呈交意見書的「團體名單」刪去香港眾志和六個團體的名字，包括西藏人權民主中心、無代表國家和人民組織、維吾爾人權項目、南蒙古人權信息中心和世界維吾爾代表大會。<br />\n<br />\n就此，香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒在10月25日去信聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處「普遍定期審議工作組」組長 Gianni Magazzeni，至今仍未得到回覆；而其他受影響團體向處方查詢，則獲告知：「作為聯合國大會的附屬機構，人權理事會和普遍定期審議工作組必須遵從聯合國依據大會決議及聯合國憲章的立場及宗旨，因此我們必須尊重有關國家的主權、獨立及領土完整性」。<br />\n<br />\n最終，聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處在11月2日另外公佈「團體摘要報告勘誤列表」（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/uprchina-corrigendum），將六個受影響團體重新納入「團體名單」和「團體摘要報告」，惟香港眾志繼續被排除在外，有關建議均在「團體摘要報告（訂稿）」被刪除（https://unpo.org/article/21200）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fuprchina-corrigendum%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AD%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E7%B4%8D%E5%85%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E3%80%8D%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%83%9F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%9D%87%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%88%E8%A8%82%E7%A8%BF%EF%BC%89%E3%80%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%EF%BC%88https%3A%2F%2Funpo.org%2Farticle%2F21200%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=33dd3137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/uprchina-corrigendum），將六個受影響團體重新納入「團體名單」和「團體摘要報告」，惟香港眾志繼續被排除在外，有關建議均在「團體摘要報告（訂稿）」被刪除（https://unpo.org/article/21200）。</a><br />\n<br />\n我們重申，香港眾志所遞交的意見書均符合聯合國宗旨和要求，而意見書提述的內容均有助於促進改革以改善人權狀況。我們憂慮聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處受到中國不適當的壓力而審查公民團體意見，特別是被北京政府針對的組織。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志促請聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處作公開交待，莫因中國威權體制在聯合國體系日益增長的影響力，而縱容北京刻意壓制香港的異見聲音。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志<br />\n2018年11月6日"},{"pid":"79fb4b835bb5bca3b6a68a6cb02bf2025fa57849","tid":891684,"uid":153615,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dcd3218d0269bf841943422145ce61525a0f6c","tid":891684,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62342fe1977a1439e532d824ebcce1b9026b5dca","tid":891684,"uid":152476,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:28:25.000Z","msg":"UN已成笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa50fc61b1d76473e98f2efb4c5609f44b02d0f4","tid":891684,"uid":40250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"解散喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTrump go ahead"},{"pid":"70ad283822d65e88cc089a5ece3ea2a9ccfa1517","tid":891684,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"聯合國=笑話"},{"pid":"abfc8be5211f137049517a71bfecb13ec4072dac","tid":891684,"uid":126731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:31:11.000Z","msg":"原來買通晒，唔怪得支那唔口交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0f19c97965597b5fc4a2725a154f74f48c9e39","tid":891684,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"聯合國都投共？"},{"pid":"1eead5359f4865f100542d88c444a531fe64daf6","tid":891684,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b0f19c97965597b5fc4a2725a154f74f48c9e39","tid":891684,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"聯合國都投共？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:47:29.000Z","msg":"唔算投共，不過都係垃圾"},{"pid":"993ce8849d651b962744d4dd206b4aecb911ea8c","tid":891684,"uid":153615,"